data.description: Welcome to this like-new 3 bed/2.5 bath townhome on Lake Lanier and sought after Buford School District! Just a 5 minute walk to the lake with boat dock access, and a wooded walking trail. This home has an open concept kitchen featuring a large island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a pantry, and recessed lighting. The living space is great for entertaining with laminate wood flooring and lots of natural sunlight. Relax on the private patio backing up to nature. Upstairs is an oversized master bedroom with a huge walk-in closet, separate shower and garden tub. Two spacious secondary bedrooms, a full bath, and walk-in laundry room. All it needs is your personal touch. Make an appointment for a showing today!
